import log from 'loglevel';
 
function prepareLine(prefix, args) {
  return [prefix].concat(Array.from(args));
}
 
export default {
  setLevel: function(level) { log.setLevel(level); },
 
  trace: function() { log.trace.apply(null, prepareLine('Notify T:', arguments)); },
  debug: function() { log.debug.apply(null, prepareLine('Notify D:', arguments)); },
  info: function()  { log.info.apply(null, prepareLine('Notify I:', arguments)); },
  warn: function()  { log.warn.apply(null, prepareLine('Notify W:', arguments)); },
  error: function() { log.error.apply(null, prepareLine('Notify E:', arguments)); }
};
